      <note>NAME:
set_source_repo_and_target_directory:

PART OF:
This transformation is part of export_repository_to_files. It is not meant to be run stand-alone.

PURPOSE:
This transformation servers two purposes:
1) set the source repository (and credentials)
2) compute the target directory

To specify the source repository, you&apos;ll have to edit the &quot;Set Source Repository&quot; step.

Currently, the target directory is computed according to this pattern:

&lt;user-home&gt; &#47; pdi_repo_export &#47; &lt;pdi_repo_name&gt;

The computed file system directory is made available
to the root job in the variable REPO_TARGET_DIR</note>
      <xloc>27</xloc>
      <yloc>8</yloc>
      <width>468</width>
      <heigth>247</heigth>
    </notepad>
  </notepads>
